events.name: Hands-On AI/ML Cloud Study Jam
events.description:
Join us for our Cloud Study Jam!

*FREE food and beverage* will be provided. More rewards/swag to online attendees finishing their exercises on time.

Online broadcast: https://zoom.us/j/6507777418

Directions to even room : https://www.bootupventures.com/arrival-instructions-bootup-executive-room.html

How to get Quiklabs credit
==========================
1. Click on this link: https://google.qwiklabs.com/quests/85?event=Your&utm_source=qwiklabs&utm_medium=lp&utm_campaign=studyjam
2. enter the code 1s-paloalto-2222 and press Submit,

Also get official Google training, a $55+ value, free of charge. Together we'll work through several Google Cloud labs. You will get hands-on experience with Machine Learning.

Then after our live session, you will have free access to more labs you can finish at home. Complete all labs in the quest and earn a Google-hosted badge for your online profile, and additional 30 days access to the training platform to compete any labs you want

What to bring
=============
1) Laptop with Chrome and Wifi
2) Gmail account to access google files
3) Familiarity with Google Cloud Platform (https://cloud.google.com/docs/overview/), we will give an intro session.

What to expect
===============
1) Access to Qwiklabs and one month free coupon. (https://go.qwiklabs.com/next-19-extended)
2) Code Jam (hands on programming experience) in solving an AI/ML problem.
3) Opportunity to pair program.

Agenda
=======
Intro to ML: Image Processing (https://google.qwiklabs.com/quests/85)

5:30pm - Event Starts with Snacks
6:00pm - Cloud ML Engine: Qwik Start (60 min)
7:00pm - Cloud API Explorer: Qwik Start (30 min)
7:30pm - Dinner Break (20 min)
7:50pm - Classify Images with AutoML Vision (60 min)
8:50pm - Detect Labels, Faces, and Landmarks with Vision API (45 min)
9:35pm - Break (15 min)
9:50pm - Text from Images with the Cloud ML (50 min)
10:40pm - Swag Prizes and Conclusion

Swag Prizes
============
Win More swag by uploading your badge screenshot at https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf7TOfrkAEkncjE3KntKLSzGISqj9T2-UPY90jp3JbIrs8JBA/viewform

GDG Chapter Name *
-------------> GDG Cloud Palo Alto
Chapter City *
-------------> Palo Alto
